        previous = nil,
        next = nil,
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = 'Activate the four switches.\n1. You begin on a small map with the greater part of the area blocked off. You will have to head north-east to reach the main map.\n2. The four switches are located in the west, south, north and east rooms, located at (F-8), (H-10), (H-6) and (J-8) respectively.\n3. The switches can be activated in any order and remain activated permanently.\n4. The Rune of Release appears in the center room at (H-8).',
        notes = '1. The NPC Lamiae in this assault will not attack you, however if they aggro and catch up to you they will warp you back to the starting point.\n2. The Lamiae will only aggro one person, this makes it possible to have a front runner aggro a Lamia and start running backwards, allowing another person(s) to run by safely. This is often more effective and reliable than splitting up.\n3. It is occasionally possible to escape an aggro\'d Lamia with Flee and/or movement speed+.\n4. In wider corridors it is possible to flee straight past a Lamia, getting out of range between it aggroing and warping you.\n5. It can be strategic to wait in rooms with corridors (or run back if one is approaching you) about the map for Lamiae to pass. You can easily hide behind the pillars.',
    },
    ['Counting Sheep'] = {
        id = 5,
        start_npc = nil,
        start_zone = 'Leujaoam Sanctum',
