        title = nil,
        repeatable = nil,
        previous = nil,
        next = nil,
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = 'The object of this assault is to clear all 15 hidden Qiqirn Mines.  The more mines successfully defused, the higher the AP reward.\n1. Mines are invisible and do not show up on Widescan.\n2. When a player approaches a mine, it will trigger a timer.  The player then has 30 seconds to locate the mine.\n      - Every few seconds, the bomb will emit a message indicating how close the player is to the bomb.  The possible messages are:\n:::"Kachink......" indicates the mine is somewhat near\n:::"Kachink..." indicates the mine is close\n:::"Kachink!" indicates the player is no more than a few steps away from the right location.\n      - When the player is close enough to the mine, it will appear and the player can click on the mine to defuse it.\n3. If the player fails to defuse the mine in time, it explodes for minor damage.\nWhen all 15 mines have been dealt with, either defused or detonated, the Rune of Release spawns at H-9.\nBlowing up all the mines fails the assault, you have to defuse at least one mine.',
        notes = '1. Qiqirn Miner can be avoided with Invisible (Status).',
    },
